item.title: Coyote Creek Sprint Enduro 2023
item.description: Event Overview The Coyote Creek Sprint Enduro is an American Motorcyclist Association District 36 sanctioned event run at the Metcalf OHV Park in Santa Clara County. Location Metcalf Motorcycle Park 300 Metcalf Rd. San Jose, CA 95138 Pre-Entry Links NOTE: If you need to purchase an AMA or D36 one-day event pass, you will need to do so on-site! You can still pre-enter for the race though! Family Enduro (Saturday): http://www.
